'''Ōtsuka Kofun Cluster''' (大塚古墳群) refers to the name of [[kofun clusters]] in Japan. Several kofun clusters with the same name exist in different regions.
* {{ill|Ōtsuka Kofun Cluster (Saitama City)|ja|大塚古墳群 (さいたま市)}} - A kofun cluster located in [[Saitama Prefecture]], [[Saitama City]]. * {{ill|Minami-Ōtsuka Kofun Cluster|ja|南大塚古墳群}} - A kofun cluster located in [[Kawagoe City]], Saitama Prefecture. * {{ill|Yamamuro Himezuka Kofun|lt=Ōtsuka Kofun Cluster (Sanmu)|ja|大塚古墳群}} - A kofun cluster located in [[Chiba Prefecture]], [[Sanmu City]], including {{ill|Yamamuro Himetsuka Kofun|ja|山室姫塚古墳}}. * {{ill|Ōtsuka Kofun Cluster (Ichikawa Misato Town)|ja|大塚古墳群 (市川三郷町)}} - A kofun cluster located in [[Yamanashi Prefecture]], [[Ichikawa Misato Town]]. * {{ill|Ōtsuka Kofun Cluster (Ōgaki)|ja|大塚古墳群 (大垣市)}} - Part of the {{ill|Fuwa Kofun Cluster|ja|不破古墳群}} in [[Gifu Prefecture]], [[Ōgaki City]]. * {{ill|Ōtsuka Kofun Cluster (Nagoya)|ja|大塚古墳群 (名古屋市)}} - Part of the {{ill|Shidami Kofun Cluster|ja|志段味古墳群}} in [[Aichi Prefecture]], [[Nagoya City]]. * {{ill|Kyōzuka-Ōtsuka Kofun Cluster|ja|経塚・大塚古墳群}} - A kofun cluster located in [[Kumamoto Prefecture]], [[Tamana City]]. * {{ill|Ōtsuka Kofun Cluster (Kagoshima)|ja|大塚古墳群 (鹿児島県)}} - A kofun cluster located in [[Kimotsuki Plain]], [[Kagoshima Prefecture]]. == See Also == * {{ill|8=ja|9=大塚古墳|Ōtsuka_Kofun_(disambiguation)|lt=Ōtsuka Kofun}}
